data.description: Step into a world of timeless elegance with this beautifully updated Spanish-style home nestled in the heart of Wolflin on a charming brick street.  Immerse yourself in the rich character of this home, highlighted by exquisite architectural details such as intricately carved wooden doors and wood ceilings adorned with viga beams. This home boasts more than character; it combines its timeless allure with modern comforts. New windows and a patio door invite natural light to dance through the spaces and a  new commercial grade TPO roof installed in June of 2022. Breathe in the air of pristine purity facilitated by a newly installed in-home air filtration system, ensuring a haven of freshness. The interior has been refreshed with new paint and refinished hardwoods. presenting a canvas of serenity and providing a perfect backdrop for any décor.
